channel.title: Free
channel.description:
I have one open dedi,
I can host a server on it..
It is a windows vps
You need Tightvnc and Vpn to connect to it. ( I can set up remote desktop)
You can buy a domain and I can set it up to it if you would like.
It has.
A great firewall If someone DDoS's just give me there ip if you can get, I can make it so they cant access or login no matter what even if they do use a proxy.
Or just tell me when they do DDoS I can still get the ip even if it is a proxy. (I shut down 6 DDoS'ers)
It is a 2.5ghz 512 mb ram, I forget how much bandwidth but its alot.
Etc.
If you want a hosting I can host it for a while actually as long as I want but I expect to get some of the donations since I am paying for it.
Don't worry I have no need to 'scam' your source I am already running 2 of mine on 2 different dedis and 2 different sites.
Make sure the server is good I don't want to be hosting some shitty server with 5 people on it.
I don't want no flame on here I don't care if you don't trust me because I know a lot of people do.
So contact me or pm me on here or at keithamunoz@Hotmail.com
